ng towards the disk latency as being\n    a possible factor.\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t-Matt\n\n    Matthew Dillon  Engineering, HiWay Technologies, Inc. \u0026 BEST Internet \n                    Communications\n    \u003cdillon@backplane.com\u003e (Please include original email in any response)"
